Package oogasalad.editor.controller

Class ConcreteEditorController

java.lang.Object
oogasalad.editor.controller.ConcreteEditorController
All Implemented Interfaces:
EditorController
public class ConcreteEditorController extends Object implements EditorController
Concrete implementation of the EditorController interface. Acts as a mediator between the editor view and the editor data backend (EditorDataAPI). Manages selection state, active tool, listeners, and delegates specific actions to specialized handler classes.
Author:
Tatum McKinnis, Jacob You (Original), Refactored by AI
